1 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
2 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby memorialize the United States Congress to take such
3 actions as are necessary to issue the Armed Forces Expeditionary Medal to U.S. veterans
4 who served in Honduras from 1981 to 1992.
5 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
6 presiding officers of the Senate and the House of Representatives of the Congress of the
7 United States of America and to each member of the Louisiana congressional delegation.
